You can configure systems other than Red Hat or Debian to automatically
start the glusterd daemon every time the system boots.

*To configure systems other than Red Hat or Debian*

* Add the following entry to the _/etc/rc.local_ file:<br /> +
# echo "glusterd" >> /etc/rc.local

